					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">After a quick glance, it seems the problem is in the "LoadBackground" routine. You set the pointer to $2020 to load the background when it is actually stored at $e020.
<br />Also why do you have 2 loops to load the tile and attribute data : since you're just loading data from ROM and copying it to VRAM, one loop can do it in one time.</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Life is complex: it has both real and imaginary components.</div>
