					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">I can't see anything wrong with the code. But I think I've found your error. Look at the value you wrote to $2000. You selected pattern table 0 ($0000) for the sprites and pattern table 1 ($1000) for the background. The pattern table you assigned to the background contains nothing but empty tiles, so the screen will always show the background color, no matter what you do.
<br />
<br />Set bit 3 of the value you write to $2000 to 1 and you'll see your background.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

